{"tid":715400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人行降準釋放7,000億人幣 支持「債轉股」項目","createTime":"2018-06-24T12:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T10:06:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f764968e2cec0ec198826b82e8003b0d73884460","tid":715400,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"【中國救市】人行降準釋放7,000億人幣<br />\n支持「債轉股」項目<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180624/58358218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180624%2F58358218&d=r1m0JIOvSxi2dmEmn8NxCkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9a3ed04b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180624%2F58358218&h=ec0b16d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180624/58358218</a><br />\n<br />\n人行宣佈，為進一步推進債轉股，加大對小微企業的支持力度，下月5日起，下調國有大型商業銀行、股份制商業銀行、郵政儲蓄銀行、城市商業銀行、非縣域農村商業銀行、外資銀行人民幣存款準備金率0.5個百分點。按現時內地存款基礎估算，今次放水規模近7,000億元（人幣‧下同），是次屬人行今年以來第3度降準。<br />\n<br />\n人行指出，工行（1398）、農行（1288）、中行（3988）、建行（939）、交行（3328）五家國有大型商業銀行和中信銀行（998）、光大銀行（6818）等十二家股份制商業銀行人民幣存款準備金率0.5個百分點，釋放資金約5,000億元，<span style=\"color: red;\">用於支持合法「債轉股」項目，但不支持「名股實債」和「殭屍企業」項目。</span><br />\n<br />\n人行同時下調郵儲銀行（1658）、城市商業銀行、非縣域農村商業銀行、外資銀行人民幣存款準備金率0.5個百分點，可釋放資金約2,000億元，<span style=\"color: red;\">主要用於支持相關銀行發放小微企業貸款，緩解融資難融資貴問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國務院上周三已率先披露，欲支援銀行開拓小微企業市場，運用定向降準等貨幣政策工具，增強小微信貸供給能力，加快已簽約債轉股項目落地。</span><br />\n<br />\n澳新銀行大中華區首席經濟師楊宇霆認為，內地是次降準主要是提供流動性穩定市場之用，亦相信今次措施與貿易戰陰霾有關，「影響冇人知，就算係內地政府都估算緊，所以先進行『保險式降準』，喺股市急跌後穩定軍心。」他估計今年尚有1至2次降準機會。<br />\n<br />\n記者：周家誠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590da6486d8a6fa7c4e03031cf3e6ec26e08dc3d","tid":715400,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:41:14.000Z","msg":"債轉股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515d0e8f4e3e26fdb38918790f85b971a663a084","tid":715400,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8531db577e5ba91c306259a32f7a26e2adea36a0","tid":715400,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822e0c13ca836434c72a7fb836e13be270f83cc2","tid":715400,"uid":19012,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"債轉股<br />\n<br />\n間公司破產 債主變股東<br />\n<br />\n變相你既priority 調低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係贏灑"},{"pid":"4d22bed0dbb537f9e243d42e7445f39b88e0a0b9","tid":715400,"uid":38390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T06:39:06.000Z","msg":"左手交右手再交翻左手"},{"pid":"5643eb7a3ef653392e29234c489a534a04e6eac9","tid":715400,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T06:45:59.000Z","msg":"又印7000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\